                        sling:resourceType="core/franklin/components/block/v1/block/item"
                        model="text-container-text"
                        modelFields="[text]"
                        name="Text Container Text"
                        text="&lt;p>I am usually up by 5 a.m. My mornings begin with coffee with my wife and playtime with the kids. Then one of us prepares breakfast for the kids while the other preps their school lunch and gear. Once the kids are ready to go, I head out to the office.&lt;/p>"/>
